<section id="Required_UIDs_and_GIDs" remap="TID_7853">
	<title>Required UIDs and GIDs</title>
	<para>
		oVirt requires certain User IDs and Group IDs (UIDs and GIDs) on the host system. When the <package> vdsm</package> and <package> qemu</package> packages are installed, default versions of these UIDs and GIDs are created on the host.
	</para>
	<para>
		If existing UIDs and GIDs on the host conflict with the default values used during <package> vdsm</package> and <package> qemu</package> installation, a conflict occurs.
	</para>
	<para>
		The UIDs and GIDs created by default during oVirt installation are:
	</para>
